===========================
NEWS for 0.4.0 (2015-07-01)
===========================

Changes since 0.3.0 (2014-09-01)
================================

[both]

* add function sign


Changes since 0.2.0 (2014-08-29)
================================

[both]

* add constant dblmin
* add constant dblmax
* add function round
* add function srand for setting random seed, it returns value of 0
* add function time for Unix timestamp
* add function trunc
* add -d for debugging message


Changes since 0.1.0 (2014-08-21)
================================

[both]

* add constant randmax for maximum integer for ineteger random number
* add function rand for integer random number
* add function randf for float random number, shorthand for rand / randmax
* add -h for help message

[command]

* add -V for version string

[examples]

* add f.sh: plot Y = F(X)
* add f-examples.sh: a set of examples of f.sh


Changes since 0.02718 (2001-07-11)
==================================

* compile as c99 for command and gnu99 for loadable
* make e to be both command and Bash loadable
* make possible to install and uninstall, and with prefix

[loadable]

* add -v to store result to the variable
* add -V to display version string

[examples]

* add sine.sh and sine.bc.sh


Changes since 0.0.0 (2001-07-11)
================================

* first public release
